---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Onchain AMM — Permissionless Markets">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Permissionless Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">無需許可的市場</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Onchain AMM</span><span class="lang-zh">鏈上自動化做市商</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">Traditional markets require exchange licenses, listing approvals, and market maker agreements. Onchain: create a liquidity pool and the market exists. Permissionless financial markets, 24/7.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">傳統market要exchange license、listing approval、market maker agreement。Onchain：create一個liquidity pool = market exists。Permissionless financial markets，24/7。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Metrics -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Key Metrics</span><span class="lang-zh">核心數據</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$1-2B</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Uniswap daily volume</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap日交易量</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">24/7</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">No trading hours</span><span class="lang-zh">無交易時限</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">x*y=k</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Constant product formula</span><span class="lang-zh">恆定乘積公式</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">1000s</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">New tokens daily</span><span class="lang-zh">每日新代幣</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is It -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">How It Works</span><span class="lang-zh">點樣運作？</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Smart contracts automatically quote prices using the constant product formula (x*y=k) — the more you buy, the higher the price goes. No market maker needed.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">Smart contract自動quote，constant product formula (x*y=k) — 買得多price就升，唔需要market maker。</span>
    </p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Constant Product Formula</span><span class="lang-zh">恆定乘積公式</span>
      </h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en">A pool contains two tokens (e.g., ETH + USDC). Their quantities maintain a constant product: <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x * y = k</span></span><span class="lang-zh">Pool入面有兩隻token（例如ETH + USDC），數量嘅乘積保持constant：<span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x * y = k</span></span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">When you buy Token A, the pool's Token A supply decreases while Token B increases — Token A's price rises automatically.</span><span class="lang-zh">你買Token A，pool入面Token A減少、Token B增加 → Token A price自動升。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">No orderbook needed, no market maker placing orders. The smart contract automatically quotes prices based on supply and demand.</span><span class="lang-zh">唔需要orderbook，唔需要market maker掛單，smart contract自動根據supply/demand quote price。</span></p>
        <p class="text-zinc-500"><span class="lang-en">Major venues: <span class="text-white">Uniswap</span> (Ethereum, $1–2B daily), <span class="text-white">Raydium</span> / <span class="text-white">Meteora</span> (Solana).</span><span class="lang-zh">主要venue：<span class="text-white">Uniswap</span>（Ethereum，$1-2B daily），<span class="text-white">Raydium</span> / <span class="text-white">Meteora</span>（Solana）。</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three things you can do -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Three Things You Can Do</span><span class="lang-zh">三件你可以做嘅嘢</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Trading -->
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">1</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          <span class="lang-en">Trading — Onchain Swap</span><span class="lang-zh">交易 — 鏈上兌換</span>
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en">Any token pair can be swapped, <span class="text-white font-medium">no listing requirement</span>. If someone has created a pool, it's tradeable.</span><span class="lang-zh">任何token pair都可以swap，<span class="text-white font-medium">no listing requirement</span>。只要有人create咗個pool，就trade到。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">Settlement is instant (seconds), and assets stay in your wallet — <span class="text-white font-medium">non-custodial</span>, no exchange intermediary.</span><span class="lang-zh">Settlement instant（幾秒內），assets stay in your wallet — <span class="text-white font-medium">non-custodial</span>，唔經exchange。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">Aggregators (Jupiter, 1inch) automatically find the best price, routing across multiple pools.</span><span class="lang-zh">Aggregators（Jupiter、1inch）自動幫你搵最好price，跨多個pool routing。</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- LP -->
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">2</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          <span class="lang-en">LP (Liquidity Provision) — Be the Market Maker</span><span class="lang-zh">LP（提供流動性）— 做Market Maker</span>
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en">Deposit two tokens into a pool and earn trading fees from every swap.</span><span class="lang-zh">Deposit兩隻token入pool，earn每筆swap嘅trading fee。</span></p>
        <p class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">In finance terms: long two assets + short volatility.</span><span class="lang-zh">Finance語言：long兩隻asset + short vol。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Impermanent loss</span> = the P&L of being short volatility. When one token's price moves significantly, your position is worth less than simply holding both tokens.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">Impermanent loss</span> = short vol嘅P&L。當其中一隻token price大幅move，你嘅position value低過simply hold兩隻token。</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Stable Pairs</span><span class="lang-zh">穩定幣對</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">Low fee (0.01–0.05%), steady return, minimal IL. E.g., USDC/USDT.</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">Low fee (0.01-0.05%)，steady return，minimal IL。USDC/USDT之類。</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">New Coins</span><span class="lang-zh">新幣</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">High fee (50–99%), high risk. High trading volume but tokens may go to zero.</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">High fee (50-99%)，high risk。Trading volume大但token可能歸零。</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Launchpad -->
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold">3</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
          <span class="lang-en">Launchpad — Permissionless IPO</span><span class="lang-zh">發射台 — 無需許可的IPO</span>
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">PumpFun</span> and <span class="text-white font-medium">Raydium LaunchLab</span> — anyone can launch a token in seconds.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">PumpFun</span>、<span class="text-white font-medium">Raydium LaunchLab</span> — 任何人幾秒之內launch一隻token。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">Bonding curve pricing: early buyers get lower prices, more buyers push the price up. At a certain market cap, it auto-migrates to an AMM pool — becoming a fully tradeable market.</span><span class="lang-zh">Bonding curve pricing：early buyer price低，越多人買price越高。到一定market cap自動migrate去AMM pool — 變成fully tradeable market。</span></p>
        <p class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Essentially a permissionless IPO — no underwriter, no prospectus, no lock-up period.</span><span class="lang-zh">本質上係permissionless IPO — no underwriter，no prospectus，no lock-up period。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">Thousands launch daily. 99% are junk, but some find gems.</span><span class="lang-zh">每日launch幾千隻。99%係junk，但有人喺入面搵到gems。</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TradFi Comparison -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">TradFi Comparison</span><span class="lang-zh">同傳統金融比較</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/50">
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-zinc-500 font-medium"></th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-zinc-500 font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">Traditional Market</span><span class="lang-zh">傳統市場</span>
            </th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 text-cyan-400 font-medium">
              <span class="lang-en">Onchain AMM</span><span class="lang-zh">鏈上AMM</span>
            </th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="text-zinc-400">
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Listing</span><span class="lang-zh">上市</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Exchange approval + regulatory filing</span><span class="lang-zh">交易所審批 + 監管備案</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Create pool = listed</span><span class="lang-zh">建立資金池 = 上市</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Market Making</span><span class="lang-zh">做市</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Designated MM agreement</span><span class="lang-zh">指定做市商協議</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Anyone can deposit liquidity</span><span class="lang-zh">任何人可提供流動性</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Trading Hours</span><span class="lang-zh">交易時間</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">9:30am – 4:00pm + holidays</span><span class="lang-zh">9:30am – 4:00pm + 假期</span></td>
            <td class="p-4">24/7/365</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800/30">
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Settlement</span><span class="lang-zh">結算</span></td>
            <td class="p-4">T+1 / T+2</td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Instant (seconds)</span><span class="lang-zh">即時（秒級）</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-4 text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Custody</span><span class="lang-zh">託管</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Broker/custodian holds</span><span class="lang-zh">經紀商/託管人持有</span></td>
            <td class="p-4"><span class="lang-en">Self-custody (your wallet)</span><span class="lang-zh">自託管（你自己的錢包）</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Business Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Business Use Cases</span><span class="lang-zh">商業應用場景</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Yield Generation</span><span class="lang-zh">收益生成</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Provide liquidity to earn trading fees. Stable pair LP (USDC/USDT) offers predictable, low-risk returns comparable to money market yields. Higher-risk pools can generate significantly higher returns for those with appropriate risk tolerance.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">提供流動性以賺取交易費用。穩定幣對LP（USDC/USDT）提供可預測、低風險的回報，類似貨幣市場收益。高風險池可為風險承受能力適當的投資者帶來顯著更高的回報。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Token Launch & Distribution</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣發行與分發</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Launch a token and create instant market access. No exchange listing fees, no underwriter needed. Used by projects from experimental tokens to tokenized real-world assets. The permissionless nature makes this a powerful alternative to traditional capital formation.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">發行代幣並建立即時市場准入。無需交易所上市費用，無需承銷商。從實驗性代幣到代幣化實體資產的項目都在使用。其無需許可的特性令其成為傳統資本形成的有力替代方案。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Risks -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Risks</span><span class="lang-zh">風險</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Impermanent loss</span><span class="lang-zh">無常損失</span></span> — <span class="lang-en">Price divergence between pooled tokens causes loss relative to holding. The fundamental cost of LP.</span><span class="lang-zh">池中代幣價格偏離導致相對於持有的損失。LP嘅基本成本。</span></p>
        <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Smart contract risk</span><span class="lang-zh">智能合約風險</span></span> — <span class="lang-en">Code bugs can lead to fund loss. Only use audited protocols.</span><span class="lang-zh">代碼漏洞可導致資金損失。只使用經審計的協議。</span></p>
        <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Rug pulls</span><span class="lang-zh">項目跑路</span></span> — <span class="lang-en">Permissionless means anyone can list — 99% of new tokens are worthless.</span><span class="lang-zh">無需許可意味著任何人可以上市 — 99%新代幣毫無價值。</span></p>
        <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Regulatory</span><span class="lang-zh">監管</span></span> — <span class="lang-en">Not regulated by the SFC. No investor protection.</span><span class="lang-zh">唔受SFC監管。無投資者保障。</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Getting Started -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Getting Started</span><span class="lang-zh">如何開始</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">1</p>
        <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Get a wallet</span><span class="lang-zh">建立錢包</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          <span class="lang-en">Phantom (Solana) or MetaMask (Ethereum)</span><span class="lang-zh">Phantom（Solana）或MetaMask（Ethereum）</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">2</p>
        <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Fund with SOL or ETH</span><span class="lang-zh">充值SOL或ETH</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          <span class="lang-en">Buy from a licensed VATP (HashKey, OSL)</span><span class="lang-zh">從持牌VATP購買（HashKey、OSL）</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">3</p>
        <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Use an aggregator</span><span class="lang-zh">使用聚合器</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          <span class="lang-en">Jupiter (Solana) or 1inch (Ethereum) for best prices</span><span class="lang-zh">Jupiter（Solana）或1inch（Ethereum）獲取最佳價格</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mb-2">4</p>
        <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Swap or provide LP</span><span class="lang-zh">兌換或提供流動性</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          <span class="lang-en">Start with stablecoin pairs for lower risk</span><span class="lang-zh">從穩定幣對開始以降低風險</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-cyan-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Explore other onchain products</span><span class="lang-zh">了解其他鏈上產品</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Polymarket for prediction markets. Hyperliquid for perps + pre-IPO.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Polymarket做prediction markets，Hyperliquid做perps + pre-IPO。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href={`${base}/products/polymarket`} class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-cyan-500 text-black text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Polymarket</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/hyperliquid`} class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-lg hover:border-zinc-500 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Hyperliquid</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
